Package: comspat
Type: Package
Title: comspat: An R package to analyze within-community spatial organization
        using species combinations
Version: 1.0
Author: James L. Tsakalos, Stefano Chelli, Giandiego Campetella, 
        Roberto Canullo, Enrico Simonetti and Sandor Bartha
Maintainer: James L. Tsakalos <jamestsakalos@gmail.com>
Description: Contains functions useful for analysing
        the spatial patterns of species combinations. The related measures are 
        from the Information Theory model family of Pál Juhász-Nagy. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
BugReports: https://github.com/jamestsakalos/comspat/issues
URL: https://github.com/jamestsakalos/comspat
LazyData: true
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: 
    future,
    future.apply,
    graphics,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    stats,
    testthat,
    vdiffr
Suggests: 
    covr
